org.wise.portal.domain.workgroup

Interface Workgroup

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Persistable, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    WorkgroupImpl

    public interface Workgroup
extends Persistable
    Workgroup is a group of users that work on the same run, like a team of users. It is made up of one or more users and the work is stored for the workgroup, not for the user.
    Author:
    Hiroki Terashima
